<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cadastrar</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Sora:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/userRegister.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="auth-shell">
        <section class="auth-panel">
            <div class="auth-copy">
                <span class="section-tag">Comece agora</span>
                <h1>Crie sua conta e organize tudo em um único lugar.</h1>
                <p>Um cadastro rápido para você começar a escrever, revisar e acompanhar suas ideias com mais clareza.</p>
                <ul class="auth-highlights">
                    <li>Cadastro simples e direto.</li>
                    <li>Espaço ideal para notas pessoais e profissionais.</li>
                    <li>Visual limpo para manter o foco no conteúdo.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="register-container">
                <h2>Cadastro</h2>
                <form action="/register" method="post" data-auth-form data-success-message="Cadastro concluido. Redirecionando para o login...">
                    <label for="username">Nome</label>
                    <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="Seu nome" required>

                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="voce@email.com" required>

                    <label for="password">Senha</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Crie uma senha" required>

                    <button type="submit">Cadastrar</button>
                </form>
                <p class="form-feedback" data-form-feedback hidden aria-live="polite"></p>
                <div class="links">
                    <a class="secondary-link" href="/login">Já tenho conta</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <script src="/js/authForm.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
